oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: A real photo postcard of American Red Cross nurses in parade, July 4, 1918, Paris, France.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: This real photo postcard shows an Independence Day parade of Red Cross nurses in the streets of Paris, France. The head of the column carries American and French flags.
